@startuml LetAITalkCallRuntimeSequence

title LetAITalk - Inbound Call Runtime Flow
autonumber

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam ArrowColor #30475E
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #30475E
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #30475E
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #AAB7C4
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam BoxBorderColor #30475E
skinparam BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #C9B458
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFBEA

actor Caller
participant "Telephony Provider" as Telephony

box "Go Real-Time Backend" #F8FAFC
participant "Go Edge\nWebhook + Media Gateway + Session Manager" as GoEdge
participant "Call Event Publisher" as Publisher
end box

box "Python AI Runtime" #F8FAFC
participant "AI Runtime\nOrchestrator + STT + Policy + LLM + Validator + TTS" as AIRuntime
participant "Post-Call Worker" as Worker
end box

participant "AI Providers\nSTT / LLM / TTS APIs" as AIProviders
database "Runtime State\nRedis + PostgreSQL" as DataLayer
collections "Artifacts\nObject Storage" as Storage
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
actor User

note right of GoEdge
Owns:
- inbound webhooks
- call session lifecycle
- media stream transport
- low-latency audio handling
end note

note right of AIRuntime
Owns:
- transcript processing
- deterministic policy checks
- bounded LLM generation
- response validation
- speech synthesis coordination
end note

== 1. Call Setup ==

Caller -> Telephony : dial LetAITalk number
Telephony -> GoEdge : inbound call webhook
GoEdge -> DataLayer : create call session\ninitialize runtime state
GoEdge -> Telephony : answer call\naccept media stream
Telephony -> GoEdge : open live audio stream

== 2. Live Conversation Loop ==

loop For each caller turn
  Telephony -> GoEdge : caller audio frames
  GoEdge -> AIRuntime : stream caller audio
  AIRuntime -> AIProviders : STT request
  AIProviders --> AIRuntime : partial / final transcript

  alt Deterministic rule is sufficient
    AIRuntime --> GoEdge : approved scripted response audio
  else LLM response is required
    AIRuntime -> AIProviders : LLM inference request
    AIProviders --> AIRuntime : candidate response text
    AIRuntime -> AIProviders : TTS synthesis request
    AIProviders --> AIRuntime : synthesized response audio
    AIRuntime --> GoEdge : validated assistant audio
  end

  GoEdge --> Telephony : outbound audio stream
  Telephony --> Caller : assistant response
  AIRuntime -> DataLayer : append transcript events\nupdate conversation state
end

== 3. Call Completion ==

Telephony -> GoEdge : call completed webhook
GoEdge -> Publisher : publish call completed event
Publisher -> Worker : start post-call processing

== 4. Post-Call Processing ==

Worker -> DataLayer : save summary\nintent\naction items
Worker -> Storage : store artifacts\nrecording references
Worker -> Notification : send post-call update
Notification -> User : push / SMS / WhatsApp

note over DataLayer
Redis is used for transient live session state.
PostgreSQL remains the permanent system of record.
end note

@enduml
